1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
ظآزA little bit sorry for my love for youظآز

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
ظآزSorry, I was a little lateظآز

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
ظآزI really want the unconscious longing
to appear fasterظآز

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
ظآزCan I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once moreظآز

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
ظآزHolding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journeyظآز

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
ظآزThe chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after anotherظآز

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
ظآزThe promised moment
will definitely not be forgottenظآز

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
ظآزCan I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeatظآز

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
ظآزStart the countdown 4321,
a new sceneryظآز

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
ظآزI want to see all the scenes about youظآز

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
ظآزNo need to miss you anymoreظآز

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
ظآزRight by your sideظآز

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:02,944
=Episode 20=

15
00:01:03,466 --> 00:01:05,300
Nobody can fire my secretary.

16
00:01:05,466 --> 00:01:06,336
Moreover,

17
00:01:07,033 --> 00:01:08,300
she is my woman.

18
00:01:11,166 --> 00:01:12,100
Try this.

19
00:01:19,666 --> 00:01:20,866
Thank you, Miss Jin.

20
00:01:22,752 --> 00:01:23,866
For what?

21
00:01:24,633 --> 00:01:26,500
I just rebuked your mom
and your grandfather.

22
00:01:26,933 --> 00:01:27,933
Now you thank me?

23
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:29,700
Are you...?

24
00:01:29,966 --> 00:01:31,300
I heard what you said.

25
00:01:34,066 --> 00:01:37,533
I was talking nonsense
just to win the argument.

26
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:39,533
I understand.

27
00:01:40,433 --> 00:01:42,866
It's reasonable
to be deeply charmed by me.

28
00:01:43,366 --> 00:01:44,200
I understand.

29
00:01:45,033 --> 00:01:45,833
Hey,

30
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:50,500
I really hate you being narcissistic.

31
00:01:56,966 --> 00:01:58,700
Sorry to interrupt.

32
00:01:58,766 --> 00:02:01,000
Here is a questionnaire.

33
00:02:01,000 --> 00:02:02,500
We hope you can fill it out

34
00:02:02,500 --> 00:02:04,066
to improve our restaurant service.

35
00:02:05,533 --> 00:02:06,333
Thank you.

36
00:02:19,400 --> 00:02:21,666
What's kind of confession
you're looking forward to the most?

37
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:33,400
It happens on a romantic rooftop,

38
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:39,300
with a light drizzle and many lights,

39
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:48,400
on a starry night.
The man I love appears with 99 roses.

40
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:54,600
Done.

41
00:02:55,933 --> 00:02:56,733
Thank you.

42
00:03:07,633 --> 00:03:09,600
Happy birthday, Miss Jin Xi'en.

43
00:03:09,966 --> 00:03:12,400
It's your favorite
Milimili macaron cake.

44
00:03:24,233 --> 00:03:25,184
Make a wish.

45
00:03:30,720 --> 00:03:31,766
Any wine?

46
00:03:55,366 --> 00:03:56,633
I'll do it myself.

47
00:04:01,166 --> 00:04:02,700
Are you okay, Miss Jin?

48
00:04:05,266 --> 00:04:06,133
Are you alright?

49
00:04:06,300 --> 00:04:07,800
I'm just thirsty.

50
00:04:09,433 --> 00:04:12,928
It's one of the last two bottles
of Lefulaite wine,

51
00:04:13,966 --> 00:04:15,133
worth 200,000 for each.

52
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:18,400
No, this is not that wine.
It's not that expensive.

53
00:04:18,833 --> 00:04:19,700
It's okay.

54
00:04:23,633 --> 00:04:26,533
I'm sorry.
I didn't know it was so expensive.

55
00:04:26,900 --> 00:04:27,800
It's okay.

56
00:04:31,233 --> 00:04:32,566
I'm going to the restroom.

57
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:40,600
It's okay. I'm not drunk.

58
00:04:43,066 --> 00:04:44,896
Miss Jin, you seem really happy.

59
00:04:49,066 --> 00:04:51,266
Why was there a survey?

60
00:04:51,633 --> 00:04:53,600
It was requested by that man.

61
00:04:53,856 --> 00:04:56,233
He had a question
for the lady who came with him.

62
00:04:56,233 --> 00:04:57,300
So romantic.

63
00:04:57,466 --> 00:05:00,733
Yeah, he even
got her a big birthday cake.

64
00:05:06,766 --> 00:05:07,566
Lan Chen.

65
00:05:10,233 --> 00:05:12,200
I was worried about you.

66
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:16,466
No, we can't.

67
00:05:19,466 --> 00:05:23,766
Today is not my birthday,
but yesterday was.

68
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:26,533
And I don't like macarons.

69
00:05:27,232 --> 00:05:29,133
That's what my younger sister likes.

70
00:05:31,328 --> 00:05:32,448
Your sister?

71
00:05:33,533 --> 00:05:35,866
Miss Jin, your sister...

72
00:05:36,275 --> 00:05:36,992
(Xi'en)

73
00:05:43,957 --> 00:05:48,800
ظآزIn a moment of awakening,
I want to escape the endless boundaryظآز

74
00:05:49,248 --> 00:05:54,272
ظآزLove is like a trap,
a carefully designed illusionظآز

75
00:05:54,592 --> 00:06:00,096
ظآزWith your name, attached to the past
that has been left behindظآز

76
00:06:03,443 --> 00:06:07,965
ظآزI pass through the crowd with youظآز

77
00:06:10,995 --> 00:06:15,956
ظآزAs if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each otherظآز

78
00:06:19,005 --> 00:06:24,829
ظآزWhen the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps inظآز

79
00:06:24,829 --> 00:06:31,296
ظآزYou come with light,
shining into my heartظآز

80
00:06:31,968 --> 00:06:35,780
ظآزStars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heartظآز

81
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:39,901
ظآزI make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting starظآز

82
00:06:39,901 --> 00:06:41,597
ظآزOpen my secretظآز

83
00:06:41,597 --> 00:06:47,645
ظآزI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for youظآز

84
00:06:47,645 --> 00:06:51,517
ظآزSinking into your love,
I want to sink deeperظآز

85
00:06:51,517 --> 00:06:56,023
ظآزWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetnessظآز

86
00:06:58,016 --> 00:07:04,733
ظآزTwo lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fateظآز
